padanya, dan yang paling penting,

00:21:47.240 --> 00:21:49.520
Lakshmi masih bersama Rishi.

00:21:49.600 --> 00:21:51.480
Jadi, tolong jangan coba-coba, kawan!

00:21:51.800 --> 00:21:53.400
Lakshmi gila!

00:21:54.040 --> 00:21:55.560
Dia gila.  Dia sudah gila!

00:21:55.640 --> 00:21:57.680
Itu sebabnya saya lebih
khawatir tentang Rishi.

00:21:57.760 --> 00:21:58.720
